Package: DGVM3D
Type: Package
Title: Simple 3D forest simulation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joerg Steinkamp
Maintainer: Joerg Steinkamp <steinkamp.joerg@gmail.com>
Description: This is a simple visualization tool for simulated vegetation
    structure/succession in space and/or time of forest gap models. Those models
    should contain either individual trees or cohorts (e.g. LPJ-GUESS: Smith et al.
    (2001, 2014)).
